name: Non Fungible Cards collection 01 - The autor
description: Hi! My name is Thiago Foresti and I'm a photographer, filmmaker and writer, among other things. This is my first attempt to explore this NFT technology , so I did this special collection of cards with some of my favorite pics. The "Non Fungible Cards" collection is an opportunity for me to explore this new art language and it is an opportunity for you to have quality tokens that may have a value increase in the long term. This first card is on me.
